    <title type="html">安装SQLite</title>
    <id> https://richeyjang.github.io/PaimengBot/PaimengBot/install/linux/sqlite/</id>
    <link href=" https://richeyjang.github.io/PaimengBot/PaimengBot/install/linux/sqlite/"/>
    <updated>2021-12-03T09:46:22.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="安装sqlite"> 安装SQLite</h1>
<h2 id="安装"> 安装</h2>
<p>若你使用的是Ubuntu，运行以下两条命令即可：</p>
<div><pre><code><span>sudo</span> <span>apt</span> <span>install</span> sqlite
<span>sudo</span> <span>apt</span> <span>install</span> libsqlite3-dev
</code></pre>
<div><span>1</span><br><span>2</span><br></div></div><h2 id="配置"> 配置</h2>
<p>随后，在派蒙Bot文件夹下的config-main.yaml配置文件中，修改db的type配置项为<code>sqlite</code>、name配置项为<code>./data/sqlite.db</code>即可。</p>
<p><img src="./../pic/sqlite.jpg" alt="sqlite" /></p>
]]></content>
